            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"奇瑞港上市過關 料籌156億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"633\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oCQxOM_S7cnu6YmJte5m0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/2f029e20-8ac0-11f0-bef6-fe9c37dbfe0e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">奇瑞港上市過關 料籌156億</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
