            "title": "美將重徵晶片關稅 蘋果豁免",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美將重徵晶片關稅 蘋果豁免\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"638\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i7diniqHbe5A0cWle_NIUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzODtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/cbab1960-8abf-11f0-be78-c6f7d2eca574\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美將重徵晶片關稅 蘋果豁免</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
